<body>
    <partial name="_NotificationsPartial" />
    <main>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div id="carousel-slider" class="carousel slide carousel-fade" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="10000">

                <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                    <li data-target="#carousel-slider" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                    <li data-target="#carousel-slider" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                    <li data-target="#carousel-slider" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                </ol>

                <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">

                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/Gym2.jpg" alt="First slide">
                    </div>

                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/Gym5.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                    </div>

                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/Gym.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="col-12 text-center mt-5">
            <h1 class="text-dark pt-4">Build with Ease</h1>
            <div class="border-top border-primary w-25 mx-auto my-3"></div>
            <p class="lead">For all of the Championes in this world!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="row my-5">
                <div class="col-md-4 my-4">
                    <img src="./images/Yogateachertraining.jpg" class="w-100" alt="" />
                    <h4 class="my-4">"In-Person Classes"</h4>
                    <p>Teaching of pop up style yoga classes from Goddess and Gods Yoga, to a powerful vinyasa flow called Powerhouse Flow, along with yin yoga, ad blindfold yoga.</p>
                    <a asp-controller="Trainer" asp-action="All" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-md">Our Team</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 my-4">
                    <img src="./images/Gym3.jpg" class="w-100" alt="" />
                    <h4 class="my-4">"Switch Beast Mode"</h4>
                    <p>Bodybuilding, a regimen of exercises designed to enhance the human body's muscular development and promote general health and fitness.</p>
                    <a asp-controller="Trainer" asp-action="All" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-md">Our Team</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 my-4">
                    <img src="./images/BoxingTraining.jpg" class="w-100" alt="" />
                    <h4 class="my-4">"Small group classes."</h4>
                    <p>Small group training is a unique way to help hoan your boxing skills and overall conditioning in a more personalized setting.Mitt work will help teach the proper boxing fundamentals.</p>
                    <a asp-controller="Trainer" asp-action="All" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-md">Our Team</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="fixed-background">

            <div class="row text-light py-5">
                <div class="col-12 text-center">
                    <h1>PROMO!</h1>
                    <h3 class="py-4" style="color: aqua">Sport Massage!</h3>
                    <h1>35 min/ 35 $</h1>
                    <h3 style="color: yellow">For Reservations: 555-123-456</h3>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="fixed-wrap">
                <div class="fixed">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>

</body>




